title: Georgetown's L.J. Peak jumps over 6-foot-10 Jessie Govan
text:
Georgetown's L.J. Peak jumps over 6-foot-10 Jessie Govan FOX Sports 
Oct 16, 2015 at 10:33p ET + 
L.J. Peak cleared his teammate for the one-handed dunk. Godofredo Vasquez-USA TODAY Sports   10:33p ET 
Friday night the Georgetown held the 2015 Hoya Hoops Madness from McDonough Arena. 
During the event's dunk contest, sophomore guard L.J. Peak (listed at 6-foot-5) jumped over 6-foot-10 freshman Jessie Govan for a one-handed dunk. true â€” Georgetown Hoyas (@georgetownhoyas) October 17, 2015 
Peak started all but one game his freshman season, averaging 7.9 points and 2.3 rebounds per contest.
